She can see dead peopleshe just chooses to ignore them. Thats Mikos plan, anyway, but it doesnt seem to be working for her in this love letter to the horror genre that will send shivers down your spineand occasionally tickle your funny bone.
(Source: Funimation)

Eren and his companions in the 104th are assigned to the newly-formed Levi Squad, whose assignment is to keep Eren and Historia safe given Eren's newly-discovered power and Historia's knowledge and pedigree. Levi and Erwin have good reason to be concerned, because the priest of the Church that Hanji had hidden away was found tortured to death, making it clear that the Military Police are involved with the cover-up. Things get more harrowing when the MPs make a move on Erwin and the Levi Squad narrowly avoids capture. Eren is also having problems with his Titan transformation, and a deadly killer has been hired to secure Eren and Historia, one Levi knows all too well from his youth.
(Source: Anime News Network)
Takane-san, Kimi no Koto Sukirashii yo

"I heard that Takamine-san likes you."
The head of the school discipline committee, Kengo Mashima, heard a rumor from an unknown source...... It turned out that the source was none other than Takamine-san herself, who wanted Mashima-kun to show more interest in her! But the overly serious Mashima-kun didn't get the hint: ......
"Saki Takamine, I heard you have a crush on me?"
"Why are you asking me for? ......!"
Actually, Mashima-kun liked Takamine-san, too. The first time you see these two, you'll be writhing in frustration at their innocent denseness!
(Source: Gagaga Bunko, translated)
Unmei de Musubareta Koibito......no Azatoi Imouto to Issen wo Koeteshimau, Ano Hi made

"If we reunite, let's be lovers"
That was the promise I made with my childhood friend, Mitsuha Mahiru a long time ago.
In the spring of my second year in high school, our fateful reunion happened. We exchanged our unchanging feelings and officially became a couple.
Just when I thought we could cohabitate blissfully at my place, another housemate - Mahiru's younger sister, Saya joined.
One night, I was kissed by Saya, who sneaked into my room.
"Shhh...be quiet. Let's keep this a secret"
From that moment, the cohabitation of three filled with secrecies began - till the day I eventually crossed the line with my lover's sister.
